OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Are we treated this way   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbecause we're on benefits?'
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Residents at a social housing estate   
OL,6, have said they are living in fear over 
OL,7, their children's health due to major   
OL,8, structural issues with their houses.   
OL,10,FThe majority of those living in        
OL,11,FKillaire Wood Lane in Bangor, County   
OL,12,FDown, are families, and many deal with 
OL,13,Fcomplex mental and physical needs.     
OL,15,FBut some have been left to live with   
OL,16,Fcrumbling door frames and water damage.
OL,18,F"If we weren't on benefits would we be 
OL,19,Ftreated this way? I doubt it," resident
OL,20,FLeigh Corbett told BBC News NI.        
